{"tid":998485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【流感高峰】屯門醫院醫生︰不少人一持有單程證　即來醫院洗腎","createTime":"2019-01-28T04:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T23:18:18.000Z","uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c7cb756be66452fec89f3056c4f32b9958ddf4","tid":998485,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:18:32.000Z","msg":"正值流感高峰期，公營醫院爆滿，醫護人員工作壓力「爆煲」。屯門醫院心臟專科醫生黃任匡表示，近幾年來，醫院的單程證病人愈來愈多，香港出生率愈來愈低，但醫院迫爆，可見是人口政策問題。<br />\n他表示，並不是鼓勵大家歧視新移民，認為不是新香港人、舊香港人的問題，醫護都是一視同仁，一樣以救人為先，但每年多5萬個新移民，質疑這種無上限的人口添加，對香港醫療系統是否負責任。"},{"pid":"6d75a0d3d1d8cd2c3ca10d883cca1217a0b1c73c","tid":998485,"uid":50526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"醫生︰不少人一持有單程證　即來醫院洗腎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/chFzLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/chFzLS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"059643c1f6a54c603ae50e06a12d2c07e4fc714e","tid":998485,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143a11496a78afe73925fee31595df289b9cf467","tid":998485,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d75a0d3d1d8cd2c3ca10d883cca1217a0b1c73c","tid":998485,"uid":50526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"醫生︰不少人一持有單程證　即來醫院洗腎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/chFzLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/chFzLS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:08:21.000Z","msg":"專門開間私家腎科醫院應該幾好賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db116fd171c7a1bde5af0c6905bd574dd9063ebb","tid":998485,"uid":180712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2c9fbf136bdbcf99ed7bf52363303fb4bb734f8","tid":998485,"uid